bridges.base

Class SLelement<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • bridges.base.Element<E>
      • bridges.base.SLelement<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class SLelement<E>
extends Element<E>
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    This class can be used to instantiate Singly List Elements with identifiers (automatically generated), labels (derived from the values of E or manually set) next pointers an object of E data type: integer, string, Tweet, Actor, Movie, EarthquakeTweet element visualizer objects containing all the CSS atributes (color, shape, opacity, size) necessary for displaying them in a web browser
